name: Sajid Mohammad
topdescription: From Karnataka, Bengaluru. I'm Experienced Full Stack Developer with a strong background in all phases of the software development lifecycle, including analysis, design, development, and deployment. Proficient in building secure and scalable web applications with a focus on the MEAN stack (MongoDB/MSSQL/MySQL, Express.js, Angular, Node.js).

servicescontainer.s_des: Specialized in developing dynamic and responsive front-end applications using Angular (versions 9 to 16), Angular Material, and Tailwind CSS. Expertise in creating scalable web applications with enhanced user experience.
Creative graphic designer skilled in crafting visually appealing designs, including logos, banners, and social media creatives, using tools like Photoshop and Canva.
Proficient in building server-side applications and APIs with Node.js, Express.js, and MongoDB. Experienced in creating scalable and secure back-end solutions.
Web designers craft the overall vision & plan for a website layout. Professional logo development: Business, Company, or Personal.
Experienced in full-cycle development of web applications using the MEAN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, Angular, and Node.js). Skilled in integrating front-end and back-end seamlessly.
Versatile developer proficient in building end-to-end web applications, combining front-end and back-end expertise to deliver robust and scalable solutions.
